verbose_text: Moreover, water pipe smoking has been linked with pathological conditions such as greater inflammation, candidiasis, periodontitis, dry socket, elevated blood chromium and nickel levels, premalignant lesions, oral cancer, oesophageal squamous cell carcinoma, attic retraction, oedema in the vocal cords, and lower habitual vocal pitch and voice turbulence index [XREF_BIBR, XREF_BIBR].
